query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## List Distinct Locations in a GRN
  แสดงรายการตำแหน่งจัดเก็บแบบไม่ซ้ำที่มีการรับสินค้าในใบรับสินค้าพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและตัวกรอง

  Lists all distinct locations where items were received on a GRN with pagination and filtering.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `grn_id` | string (UUID) | Good Received Note ID |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `search` | string | No | — | Full-text search |
  | `searchfields` | string | No | `location_code,location_name` | Comma-separated fields to search |
  | `filter` | string | No | — | Comma-separated `field:value` pairs |
  | `sort` | string | No | `location_code:asc` | Comma-separated `field:asc\|desc` |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `procurement.goods_received_note:view`
  - **Roles**: HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "location_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "location_code": "WH-MAIN",
        "location_name": "Main Warehouse"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 1,
      "total": 1,
      "prev": null,
      "next": null
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `procurement.goods_received_note:view` permission |
  | 404 | Good Received Note not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

params:path {
  grn_id: 04e065de-03d0-4f33-baee-3ca3f7823eea
